39;re on your way.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eYou can also gain access to live TV services as well, and the remote even supports voice controls using Amazon\u0026#39;s Alexa. You can even control compatible smart home products as well. Overall, not a bad purchase for just $20, especially if you\u0026#39;re looking to take your monitor or TV to a new level.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eThe great part is that once you\u0026#39;re done with watching your shows, you just switch over your input to a new source, and you\u0026#39;re back to your normal monitor experience. It doesn\u0026#39;t get any easier or cheaper than this, which is why it\u0026#39;s a great time to pick up an Amazon Fire TV Stick.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                                            \n\n\n\n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
